data.revised_prompt: Generate a professional, high-quality image of a cocktail deemed 'Tropical Creamy Herb Elixir.' The cocktail, in a chic, towering highball glass, layers a creamy shade with gilded undertones hailing from dark rum and pineapple juice. The shimmering surface of this delightful elixir is adorned with a basil leaf overlapping with a slender lime wheel. The ambient light graces the scene with a mild luminosity, casting subtle reflections onto the glass that are amplified by a single glimmering ice cube sailing within. The background, an ethereal blur of an equatorial jungle interspersed with bursts of sunlight, offers a vibrant yet soothing setting. Highlight the cocktail's composition of 2 oz Dark Rum, 1 oz Coconut Cream, 1 oz Fresh Pineapple Juice, 0.5 oz Lime Juice, 0.25 oz Agave Syrup, 4 Fresh Basil Leaves, and 1 Dash Angostura Bitters. Go for a clear backdrop with soft focus and a photorealistic style devoid of any text or watermarks, making it look as if it was snapped by a skilled food photographer.
